* View Data Lineage\nusing Catalog Explorer
** Navigation
***_ Catalog → table → Lineage tab
***_ See Lineage Graph button
***_ Interactive visualization
** Graph features
***_ Tables as nodes, arrows = data flow
***_ Expand upstream/downstream (+)
***_ Connection details panel
** Column-level lineage
***_ Select column to trace
***_ Upstream contributing columns
***_ Downstream derived columns
** Job & Dashboard lineage
***_ Jobs tab → Downstream
***_ Dashboards tab
***_ Impact analysis before schema changes
@endmindmap
